$ Oracle: ANSI Joins
@ ANSI join

sa:

  Traditional joins are sometimes preferred over ANSI joins because ANSI joins
    • prevent the application of → development/databases/Oracle/SQL/hints#ora-global-hint-ansi-join[global hints]
    • might be the cause for → development/databases/Oracle/errors/ORA-12054_cannot-set-the-ON-COMMIT-refresh-attribute-for-the-materialized-view errors when trying to be used in → development/databases/Oracle/objects/views/materialized[materialized views].
